    <b>Introduction to HTML</b><br><br>

    HTML (<i>Hypertext Markup Language</i>) is used to create document on the <u>World Wide Web</u>.<i>It is simply a collection of certain key words called "Tags" that are helpful in writing the document to be displayed using a browser on Internet.</i>  HTML was developed by <b>Tim Berners-Lee</b> in 1992.
